name: Doggensnout Skeptic
description: The Doggensnout Skeptic is a digital collectible and cryptocurrency project inspired by a character created by Matt Furie, the renowned artist behind Pepe the Frog. Specifically named the "Pepe Predator" by Furie, the Doggensnout Skeptic is positioned as the predator of Matt Furie's Boys Club, including the iconic Pepe the Frog. This community-driven initiative aims to attract collectors and investors in the digital and meme culture space by leveraging the unique appeal of Furie's characters.
